title: Savage Garden And Darren Hayes Collection - Release Three
description:
A year later...

Sorry for all the delay in getting the next release out! Since the last release, I have re-added the Signal One performance as requested by b33znutz from ThePirateBay, and also added 5 extra songs by Darren Hayes (including I Wish You Heaven, as requested by nugut on Mininova), as well as an interview including two live acoustic performances of On The Verge Of Something Wonderful and Insatiable. And of course, Darren Hayes' newest album, This Delicate Thing We've Made.

Enjoy!
